reviews.title: You long for that back
reviews.text:
What a great case. Delicious Ribeye on, never tasted so tender before. The site dishes are also delicious and fresh. The service is of paramount importance here and staff g friendly and service oriented, you never have to ask for attention and ensure an atmospheric evening. We sat down after dinner at the cozy bar, and had a lot of fun. 
Aviation also looks great, and there is always sandwiches and soup of the week. Very diverse and tasty 😋

reviews.title: Always cozy and tasty at Meat Franky's!
reviews.text:
We come to Meat Franky's every now and then and it's always good, really. The atmosphere is cozy and the restaurant is always full, which creates a lively atmosphere. Occasionally there is live music from the bar, which gives a nice extra touch to the evening.

The food is always delicious – well prepared, tasteful and with plenty of choice. Whether you’re here for a sumptuous dinner or just a good steak, you’ll be fine.

In short: a must to try if you are in the area!
⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
